OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid in Wales: Exam help  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto continue for GCSEs,     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FA-levels                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Changes to exams brought in during the 
OL,6, Covid pandemic will continue in Wales  
OL,7, next year, the exam watchdog has said. 
OL,9,FQualifications Wales said pupils will  
OL,10,Fagain get advance information about the
OL,11,Fcontent of tests in 2022-23.           
OL,13,FIt will give those sitting GCSEs, AS   
OL,14,Fand A-Levels an indication of topics,  
OL,15,Fthemes and texts to help them prepare. 
OL,17,FThe regulator's chief executive Philip 
OL,18,FBlaker said the pandemic was still     
OL,19,Fhaving a "substantial impact on        
OL,20,Fteaching and learning".                
